PLUGINS PARA REACT NATIVE, REMOVER OS ERROS DE LINT AO USAR PROPRIEDADES
DE BOX SHADOW

"plugins": [
      {
        "name": "typescript-styled-plugin",
        "lint": {
          "validProperties": [
            "shadow-color",
            "shadow-opacity",
            "shadow-offset",
            "shadow-radius",
            "padding-horizontal",
            "padding-vertical",
            "margin-vertical",
            "margin-horizontal",
            "tint-color",
            "aspect-ratio",
            "elevation"
          ]
        }
      }
    ]

OS PLUGINS VEM DENTRO DO COMPILER OPTIONS
"compilerOptions": {
    "strict": true,
    "baseUrl": "./src",
    "paths": {
      "@/*": ["./*"]
    },
    "plugins": []
  }
